data.description: Wonderful 4/3/2 on cul-de-sac lot backing up to greenbelt. Conveniently located near Lackland AFB, Kelly Field, and Sea World, this gem has gas cooking and a tankless water heater. The game room upstairs will quickly become your favorite room! This is one of the largest lots in the neighborhood that is well-suited for outdoor entertaining and activities.
